
  Torchic    Fire Type Pokémon

  TORCHIC sticks with its TRAINER, 
  following behind with unsteady 
  steps.  Torchic breathes 
  fire of over 1,800 degrees F, 
  including fireballs that leave 
  the foe scorched black. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Torchic ► Combusken ► Blaziken

